# signalk-dmi environment template — copy to .env (which is gitignored).
#
# The current DMI Open Data host (opendataapi.dmi.dk) is KEY-FREE — no secret is
# required to run this plugin. This template exists only so that IF DMI ever
# reintroduces an API key (the retired dmigw.govcloud.dk host required one), you
# have somewhere to put it without changing code.
#
# DMI_API_KEY=your-key-here-if-ever-required
